OL,6, A group of charities has sounded the
OL,7, alarm over the growing use of
OL,8, buy-now-pay-later to buy goods.
OL,10,FCitizens Advice, a network of legal,
OL,11,Fmoney and consumer groups, said many
OL,12,Fusers were getting into debt and
OL,13,Fstruggling to pay for food and bills.
OL,15,FBuy-now-pay-later (BNPL) is
OL,16,Fincreasingly popular among young people
OL,17,Fbuying online, and at some High Street
OL,18,Foutlets.
OL,20,FHowever, Citizens Advice said many
OL,21,Fconsumers regretted using it.
